maintext:
INDIANAPOLIS (AP) _ The winning numbers in Sunday afternoon’s drawing of the Indiana Lottery’s “Quick Draw Midday” game were:
07-09-13-15-17-20-22-23-27-29-32-42-44-49-57-58-66-67-68-77, BE: 15
(seven, nine, thirteen, fifteen, seventeen, twenty, twenty-two, twenty-three, twenty-seven, twenty-nine, thirty-two, forty-two, forty-four, forty-nine, fifty-seven, fifty-eight, sixty-six, sixty-seven, sixty-eight, seventy-seven; BE: fifteen)
